Safety constraints:
- Preserve MPI message matching, rank/tag/communicator semantics, and ordering requirements.
- Only recommend overlap if overlapped compute does not read incomplete receive buffers.
- Only recommend checkpoint/recovery changes at safe phase boundaries.
- Keep the change local and reversible.

